---
Brutal squirrel v0.4
---
This is converter to hex digits (plain text) and back.
Using it you can use your favourite text editor (such as vi or emacs)
as hex editor. Also you can compose any binary file or text file with
non-keyboard symbols directly at hex digits.

Reads from standart input and puts to standart output.

Options:
-c - compile binary file
-d - decompile to hex digits
-t - text (void newline symbol before EOF)
-b - binary (default)
-h/--help - help
